bib_record.title: Differential cross sections for the (n,a) reactions induced by 14 and 18 MeV neutrons in some rare-earth nuclei

free_txt: Leopoldyana Glowacka, Military Univ. of Tech., Warsaw
Lucjan Zemlo, Inst. of Nuclear Research, Warsaw
Energy scale calibration was performed using alphas
from ThC (6.05 MeV), ThC' (8.78 MeV) and from
the FWHM of the resolution curve.
The neutron flux was measured by counting the recoil
protons from a thin polyethylene foil.
The absolute calibration of the monitor was performed
by measuring the 847 keV gamma transition in 56Fe
Oxydes deposited on thick carbon backing
